name: Industry 5.0
description:
We are living in a world of overconsumption. But behind that, companies are cutting job to meet our demand. For the few remaining employees, they are treating like beasts, because for companies is all about money and competition. Production is running 24 hours a day, and employees are monitored around the clock. This is the industry 5.0.

This piece has been created on Procreate Pocket. Sketch and timelapse are available on request !
